values: well here are my seven songs: 1) Tristania - tender trip on earth I love Vibekes voice on this track..haunting/beautiful! 2) Counting Crows - Colourblind I love the whole Cruel intentions soundtrack but this is currently my favourite! 3) Sisters of mercy - Temple of love A classic! 4) Mary J Blige - Be without you I love the whole vibe of this song and Mary has a great voice! 5) Leaves eyes - Returning to life One of my 'best' Leaves eyes songs! 6) NIN ft David Bowie - Hurt What can I say..Trent and David..musical genius combined!and this song is so powerful 7) VAST - Flames Just a beautiful song!
